            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Actually, a simpler solution:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlspconfig.clangd.setup({\r\n  root_dir = function(fname)\r\n    return lspconfig.util.root_pattern({'compile_commands.json'})(fname)\r\n  end,\r\n  single_file_support = false\r\n})\r\n```\r\nSetting `root_dir` required because by default clangd searches for everything related to C/C++ stack, including .git.",
